<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Footer</title>
</head>
<body>
    <footer
        style="background: #0f172a; color: #94a3b8; padding: 80px 10% 30px; font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, sans-serif; position: relative; overflow: hidden;">
        <div
            style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 2px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, #3b82f6, #8b5cf6, #ec4899);">
        </div>

        <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr)); gap: 50px;">

            <div>
                <h2 style="color: #ffffff; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 16px; letter-spacing: -0.5px; display:flex; align-items:center; gap:10px;">
                    <span style="background:#2563eb; border-radius:8px; width:34px; height:34px; display:inline-flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; font-size:16px;"><i class="fa-solid fa-book-open"></i></span>
                    <span style="color:#ffffff;">Vidhya</span><span style="color:#60a5fa;">Litee</span>
                </h2>
                <p style="line-height: 1.6; font-size: 15px; margin-bottom: 25px;">
                    Leading the digital transformation of educational institutions with smart automation and seamless
                    management tools.
                </p>
                <div style="display: flex; gap: 15px;">
                    <a href="#" style="color: #fff; font-size: 18px; opacity: 0.7; transition: 0.3s;"><i
                            class="fab fa-linkedin"></i></a>
                    <a href="#" style="color: #fff; font-size: 18px; opacity: 0.7; transition: 0.3s;"><i
                            class="fab fa-twitter"></i></a>
                    <a href="#" style="color: #fff; font-size: 18px; opacity: 0.7; transition: 0.3s;"><i
                            class="fab fa-instagram"></i></a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div>
                <h4
                    style="color: #ffffff; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 25px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px;">
                    Company</h4>
                <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; line-height: 2.2; font-size: 15px;">
                    <li><a href="/privacy-policy" style="color: inherit; text-decoration: none; transition: 0.3s;"
                            onmouseover="this.style.color='#3b82f6'" onmouseout="this.style.color='inherit'">Privacy
                            Policy</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/terms-conditions" style="color: inherit; text-decoration: none; transition: 0.3s;"
                            onmouseover="this.style.color='#3b82f6'" onmouseout="this.style.color='inherit'">Terms &
                            Conditions</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/terms-conditions" style="color: inherit; text-decoration: none; transition: 0.3s;"
                            onmouseover="this.style.color='#3b82f6'" onmouseout="this.style.color='inherit'">Refund
                            Policy</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div>
                <h4
                    style="color: #ffffff; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 25px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px;">
                    Support</h4>
                <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 15px;">
                    <div style="width: 35px; color: #3b82f6;"><i class="fas fa-envelope"></i></div>
                    <span style="font-size: 15px;">harshitagarg2295@gmail.com</span>
                </div>
                <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 15px;">
                    <div style="width: 35px; color: #3b82f6;"><i class="fas fa-phone-alt"></i></div>
                    <span style="font-size: 15px;">+91 6263824989</span>
                </div>
                <div style="display: flex; align-items: start;">
                    <div style="width: 35px; color: #3b82f6; margin-top: 3px;"><i class="fas fa-map-marker-alt"></i>
                    </div>
                    <span style="font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.4;">Madhopura Gali No. 6,<br>Morena, MP, 476001</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div
            style="margin-top: 60px; padding-top: 30px; border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05); display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; font-size: 14px;">
            <p>© 2025 VidhyaLitee. Owned & Managed by <strong>Harshita Garg</strong>.</p>
            <p style="opacity: 0.5;">Designed with ❤️ for Education</p>
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>

</html>